General.Name: Toys R Us ANZ Limited
General.Description: ToysRUs ANZ Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in distribution of toys and hobbies in Australia and New Zealand. It also owns and operates e-commerce websites, such as ToysRUs, BabiesRUs, and Hobby Warehouse. The company was formerly known as Funtastic Limited and changed its name to ToysRUs ANZ Limited in June 2021. ToysRUs ANZ Limited was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
